Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.32,Ed - Ro,ED,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1\blur3}Mirai no Kawari ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.32,Ed - Tl,ED,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)\be1\blur3}a ochránit budoucnost
